==English==
===Etymology===
Portuguese ''madeira'' "wood", from Latin [[materia]].  

===Proper noun===
'''Madeira'''

Island in the [[Atlantic Ocean]] and an autonomous region of [[Portugal]].

===Noun===
'''madeira'''

A fortified wine made in Madeira.

